{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2581120/extras/Key_Art_RevisedWIP-15.png?t=1739718647\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2581120/extras/Gif5.gif?t=1739718647\" />Fight and lead your army from a ground level view of large fantasy battles, command your formation of troops, and direct your forces through hack-and-slash encounters to claim ultimate victory! Go head to head in objective based conquest mode. Test your defensive skills in a wave based survival mode, or employ grand strategy in a campaign mode. Varied troop types offer distinct fighting styles and weapons, allowing for diverse playstyles and tactics. Will you anchor a battle line with spearmen, shatter defenses with mighty great swords, or rain arrows upon your enemies? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2581120/extras/Key_Art_RevisedWIP-14.png?t=1739718647\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2581120/extras/Gif1.gif?t=1739718647\" />Utilize the full roster of available troop loadouts to gain victory!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Diverse Unit Arsenal:</strong> Command more than 70 troop types across 5 factions adding depth and dynamic strategies to class-based battles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Strategic Formations:</strong> Employ formation tactics by adjusting your unit's stance and formation shape while also commanding your army as a whole.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Wave Survival Siege Mode:</strong> Test your skills against increasing enemy pressure as you defend against waves of varied enemies. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Multiplayer Mayhem:</strong> Challenge your skills against AI bots or friends in local multiplayer.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Objective Based Gameplay:</strong> Battle for control of objectives and manipulate spawn points to strategically choose spawned allies.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2581120/extras/Key_Art_RevisedWIP-11.png?t=1739718647\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2581120/extras/Gif3.gif?t=1739718647\" />Objective based gameplay where you capture objectives to drain your opponent's supplies and achieve victory.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2581120/extras/Key_Art_RevisedWIP-12.png?t=1739718647\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2581120/extras/Gif2.gif?t=1739718647\" />Defend your fortification against increasing waves of enemies to survive as long as possible.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2581120/extras/Key_Art_RevisedWIP-13.png?t=1739718647\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2581120/extras/Gif4.gif?t=1739718647\" />Capture territories in an ongoing campaign to unlock additional unit types and clear your enemies from the region.</p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/2581120?t=1739718647","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2581120/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1739718647","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2581120/capsule